.DT
adjust_components
$MUDNAME$ Creator Help
adjust_components

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
adjust_components -  This function is used to adjust the quantities of components consumed by a spell.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
mixed * adjust_components(object caster,
int stage,
mixed * quant,
mixed * args)
.EI

.SH Parameters
.SI 5
%^BOLD%^caster%^RESET%^ - the person casting the spell
%^BOLD%^stage%^RESET%^ - the stage currently being executed
%^BOLD%^quant%^RESET%^ - mapping containing the components for that stage
%^BOLD%^args%^RESET%^ - the args for the spell
.EI

.SH Returns
.SI 5
mapping showing the correct components for that stage.

.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/std/effects/magic/magic_spell.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

This function is used to adjust the quantities of components consumed by
a spell. Overload it to adjust them.
.EP

